Summary: Saw a triangle shapped object blinked twice and dissappeared
divs: Sighting DetailsThis happened on Wednesday nite while I was talking to my two sons on there cell phone. They were buy carroll Iowa around 6:30 pm when the seen a triangle shaped object in the wesgtern sky it lighted up twice and then dissappeared, about 5 to 10 mins later they seen fighter jets comming from the west headed east to the are where the object was last observed. They got to there house in carroll and they said that the fighter jets flew around the town for over a hour before heading east . my youngest son headed back out and said that the jets contiuned on toward Rockwell city Iowa.
